{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Sailing Stone</strong></h2>3D roller arcade-style indie game.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Hop and Roll your way.</h2></strong> </li></ul>Avoid obstacles through 50 levels as fast as possible.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Try to beat the high score.</h2></strong> </li></ul>Become number one on the leaderboard.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Endless entertainment.</h2></strong> </li></ul>Each level is created by a procedural generation.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Make your way through 50 different levels.</h2></strong> </li></ul>There are 5 types of biomes: Desert, Plains, Forest, Canyon, and Snow. 10 levels in each world.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Find the best ways to exploit the game.</h2></strong></li></ul>You can save and load your game, you have lives along the way, and the ability to respawn.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The difficulty is <strong>incremental.</strong></h2></li></ul>You go faster and faster with each level and cannot stop until you reach the end of a level.<br>Procedural generation is getting more and more intense.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746830/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1666991903","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746830/page.bg.jpg?t=1666991903","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746830/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1666991903","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746830/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1666991903","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Sailing Stone</strong><